Value Added Information Exchange System The audits were carried out due to an on 8 July. Agreement concluded on 1 June 2006 by the Court of Auditors of the Czech Republic ("NKÚ") and the Bundesrech-nungshof ("BRH") of the Federal Republic of Germany.
The cooperation focused on the review of selected transactions between entrepreneurs of the Czech Republic and the Federal Republic of Germany, the recovery of information obtained through international assistance between financial administrations and the comparison of turnover tax management systems in the two states.
